(1, 'teaser1', 0, 'no', '2014-11-18 11:36:00', '2015-12-31 00:00:00', 'Products', '', '{"subtitle":"","link":"\\/en\\/products\\/icard","link_target":"_self","text":"<p>Shape and combine offline and online visitor experience! By using different products developed by HORISEN, you can easily reach desired business potential and engage different customers. With more than useful SMS services that are still widely-used, through always popular social media products that are proven to increase website traffic and overall conversion process (visitor to customer), we offer you modern and integrated customer loyalty system: the invisible customer card for more purchases and customer retention.<br \\/>Among numerous products, we emphasize:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n    <li><a href=\\"\\/en\\/products\\/icard\\">The new iCard customer loyalty program<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n    <li><a href=\\"\\/en\\/products\\/megapromo\\">Megapromo web campaigns<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n    <li><a href=\\"\\/en\\/products\\/smspark\\">SMS &amp; Park solution<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n    <li><a href=\\"\\/en\\/products\\/smswin\\">SMS &amp; Win as a highly-viral service <\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n    <li><a href=\\"\\/en\\/products\\/smswin\\">MFA: Facebook fan page apps <\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n    <li><a href=\\"\\/en\\/products\\/callpay\\">Call &amp; Pay: the fastest payment solution<\\/a<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li><a href=\\"\\/en\\/products\\/internet-apps\\">Intranet Apps<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>","img_960_2x":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser1\\/produkte\\/produkte_960_2x.jpg","img_960":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser1\\/produkte\\/produkte_960.jpg","img_768_2x":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser1\\/produkte\\/produkte_768_2x.jpg","img_768":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser1\\/produkte\\/produkte_768.jpg","img_480_2x":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser1\\/produkte\\/produkte_480_2x.jpg","img_480":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser1\\/produkte\\/produkte_480.jpg","img_320_2x":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser1\\/produkte\\/produkte_320_2x.jpg","img_320":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser1\\/produkte\\/produkte_320.jpg","image_alt":"Products - Horisen.com"}', NULL, 0),
(2, 'teaser2', 0, 'no', '2014-11-18 11:50:00', '2015-12-31 00:00:00', 'Telecom', '', '{"subtitle":"","link":"\\/en\\/telecom\\/bulk-sms-for-carrier","link_target":"_self","text":"<p>Your customers appreciate the convenience not only to call their family and friends, but also to consume different services, get help and support or participate in a winning game or voting campaign by simply dialing a phone number. In addition, they can pay for a service, schedule a meeting or reminder call, hear about the news or weather forecasts, and much more.<br \\/>\\r\\nHORISEN, as the best telecom-based service provider, uses the technology called Interactive Voice Response (IVR). IVR services are completely tailored to the customer profile and, therefore, significantly reduce costs and improve the customer experience. Companies are more likely to use IVR services in order to extend their business activities to 24\\/7 operation or support. And, the most important, IVR system gathers customer data very fast \\u2013 especially by using premium-rate numbers.<br \\/>\\r\\nIn addition to Telecom services, HORISEN offers Bulk SMS for Carrier \\u2013 a powerful application system that helps you conquer the mass market within a short time and spread your business worldwide. <\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n    <li><a href=\\"\\/en\\/telecom\\/bulk-sms-for-carrier\\">Bulk SMS for Carrier<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n    <li><a href=\\"\\/en\\/telecom\\/call-win\\">Call &amp; Win<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n    <li><a href=\\"\\/en\\/telecom\\/call-vote\\">Call &amp; Vote <\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n    <li><a href=\\"\\/en\\/telecom\\/number-hosting\\">Premium Number Hosting <\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>","img_960_2x":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser2\\/telecom\\/telecom_960_2x.jpg","img_960":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser2\\/telecom\\/telecom_960.jpg","img_768_2x":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser2\\/telecom\\/telecom_768_2x.jpg","img_768":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser2\\/telecom\\/telecom_768.jpg","img_480_2x":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser2\\/telecom\\/telecom_480_2x.jpg","img_480":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser2\\/telecom\\/telecom_480.jpg","img_320_2x":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser2\\/telecom\\/telecom_320.jpg","img_320":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser2\\/telecom\\/telecom_320_2x.jpg","image_alt":"Telecom - Horisen.com"}', NULL, 0),
(3, 'teaser3', 0, 'no', '2014-11-18 11:55:00', '2015-12-18 00:00:00', 'Design', '', '{"subtitle":"","link":"\\/en\\/design-graphics\\/consulting-concept","link_target":"_self","text":" <p>Design is not only about company\\u2019s logo or corporate colors anymore. Design has become a holistic view of a company regarding both visual and contextual approach. Customer loyalty is built through a quality designed brand, having in mind the whole concept and related marketing activities that provide a pure visual experience. <br \\/>\\r\\nWe deliver beyond expectations \\u2013 from professional advice, creative ideas and advertising concept approach, through corresponding storytelling and filming to monitoring and evaluation your campaign\\u2019s success. Our experts help you in creative consulting process combining offline and online media. Only with the right marketing strategy, thinking out-of-the-box and the right implementation steps, your business is on the top. <br \\/>\\r\\nHORISEN takes care of creative solutions and brand design strategies that provide a very strong business visibility. <br \\/>\\r\\nWe offer you: <\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n    <li><a href=\\"\\/en\\/design-graphics\\/consulting-concept\\">Consulting and Concept<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n    <li><a href=\\"\\/en\\/design-graphics\\/designs\\">Design Areas  <\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n    <li><a href=\\"\\/en\\/design-graphics\\/video\\">Videos <\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n    <li><a href=\\"\\/en\\/design-graphics\\/offers\\">Special Offers  <\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>","img_960_2x":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser3\\/design\\/design_960_2x.jpg","img_960":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser3\\/design\\/design_960.jpg","img_768_2x":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser3\\/design\\/design_768_2x.jpg","img_768":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser3\\/design\\/design_768.jpg","img_480_2x":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser3\\/design\\/design_480_2x.jpg","img_480":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser3\\/design\\/design_480.jpg","img_320_2x":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser3\\/design\\/design_320_2x.jpg","img_320":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser3\\/design\\/design_320.jpg","image_alt":"Design - Horisen.com"}', NULL, 0),
(4, 'teaser4', 0, 'no', '2014-11-18 13:13:00', '2015-12-31 00:00:00', 'Mobile Marketing', '', '{"subtitle":"","link":"\\/en\\/mobile-marketing\\/sms-mass-mailing","link_target":"_self","text":"<p>HORISEN is a professional mobile marketing company. We are here to give you smart advices how to use mobile marketing for your business. With our efficient and innovative mobile marketing strategies, your campaigns will lead to business development and strong brand loyalty. <br \\/>\\r\\nWith SMS you reach everyone, anytime, anywhere and immediately. Mobile phone is still the only device which allows you to communicate without delays, comparing it to contemporary technical achievements and online messaging systems. For this reason, the mobile phone is able to conquer the mass market within a short time and provide great mobile marketing opportunities, especially when using different SMS applications.<br \\/>\\r\\nMobile marketing helps you in cross-media campaigns by integrating traditional and online advertising channels using an efficient strategy. This strategy includes automated tools for superior campaign performance:<\\/p> \\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n    <li><a href=\\"\\/en\\/telecom\\/bulk-sms-for-carrier\\">Bulk SMS <\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n    <li><a href=\\"\\/en\\/mobile-marketing\\/sms-newsletter\\">SMS Newsletter  <\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n    <li><a href=\\"\\/en\\/mobile-marketing\\/sms-winning-game\\">SMS&amp;Win <\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n    <li><a href=\\"\\/en\\/mobile-marketing\\/sms-voting\\">SMS&amp;Vote  <\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n    <li><a href=\\"\\/en\\/mobile-marketing\\/premium-sms\\">Premium SMS <\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n    <li><a href=\\"\\/en\\/mobile-marketing\\/inbound-sms-service\\">Inbound SMS Service  <\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n    <li><a href=\\"\\/en\\/mobile-marketing\\/pay-by-sms\\">SMS&amp;Pay <\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>","img_960_2x":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser4\\/mobile-marketing\\/mobile_marketing_960_2x.jpg","img_960":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser4\\/mobile-marketing\\/mobile_marketing_960.jpg","img_768_2x":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser4\\/mobile-marketing\\/mobile_marketing_768_2x.jpg","img_768":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser4\\/mobile-marketing\\/mobile_marketing_768.jpg","img_480_2x":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser4\\/mobile-marketing\\/mobile_marketing_480_2x.jpg","img_480":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser4\\/mobile-marketing\\/mobile_marketing_480.jpg","img_320_2x":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser4\\/mobile-marketing\\/mobile_marketing_320_2x.jpg","img_320":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser4\\/mobile-marketing\\/mobile_marketing_320.jpg","image_alt":"Moblie Marketing - Horisen.com"}', NULL, 0),
(5, 'slider-main', 0, 'no', '2014-11-18 13:18:00', '2015-12-18 00:00:00', 'Slider image 1', '', '{"link":"","link_target":"_self","css_id":"","css_text":"","img_1366":"\\/images\\/slider\\/slider-main\\/horisen\\/horisen_1366.jpg","img_960_2x":"\\/images\\/slider\\/slider-main\\/horisen\\/horisen_960_2x.jpg","img_960":"\\/images\\/slider\\/slider-main\\/horisen\\/horisen_960.jpg","img_768_2x":"\\/images\\/slider\\/slider-main\\/horisen\\/horisen_768_2x.jpg","img_768":"\\/images\\/slider\\/slider-main\\/horisen\\/horisen_768.jpg","img_480_2x":"\\/images\\/slider\\/slider-main\\/horisen\\/horisen_480_2x.jpg","img_480":"\\/images\\/slider\\/slider-main\\/horisen\\/horisen_480.jpg","img_320_2x":"\\/images\\/slider\\/slider-main\\/horisen\\/horisen_320_2x.jpg","img_320":"\\/images\\/slider\\/slider-main\\/horisen\\/horisen_320.jpg","image_alt":"Horisen slider image"}', NULL, 0),
(6, 'slider-main', 0, 'no', '2014-11-18 13:18:00', '2015-12-18 00:00:00', 'Slider image 2', '', '{"link":"","link_target":"_self","css_id":"","css_text":"","img_1366":"\\/images\\/slider\\/slider-main\\/horisen2\\/horisen2_1366.jpg","img_960_2x":"\\/images\\/slider\\/slider-main\\/horisen2\\/horisen2_960_2x.jpg","img_960":"\\/images\\/slider\\/slider-main\\/horisen2\\/horisen2_960.jpg","img_768_2x":"\\/images\\/slider\\/slider-main\\/horisen2\\/horisen2_768_2x.jpg","img_768":"\\/images\\/slider\\/slider-main\\/horisen2\\/horisen2_768.jpg","img_480_2x":"\\/images\\/slider\\/slider-main\\/horisen2\\/horisen2_480_2x.jpg","img_480":"\\/images\\/slider\\/slider-main\\/horisen2\\/horisen2_480.jpg","img_320_2x":"\\/images\\/slider\\/slider-main\\/horisen2\\/horisen2_320_2x.jpg","img_320":"\\/images\\/slider\\/slider-main\\/horisen2\\/horisen2_320.jpg","image_alt":"Horisen slider image 2"}', NULL, 0),
(7, 'intro-slider', 0, 'no', '2014-11-18 13:40:00', '2015-12-18 00:00:00', 'On our way to <span class="bold">success</span>', '', '{"subtitle":"Since 2001 we\\u2019ve been working on bringing all digital communication channels under one umbrella to make a single, cross-media channel.","link":"\\/en\\/home","link_target":"_self","button_text":"Learn more","css_id":"","css_text":"","img_p":"\\/images\\/slider\\/intro-slider\\/intro-image-1\\/intro-image-1_l.jpg","img_l":"\\/images\\/slider\\/intro-slider\\/intro-image-1\\/intro-image-1_l.jpg","img_1920":"\\/images\\/slider\\/intro-slider\\/intro-image-1\\/intro-image-1_l.jpg","image_alt":"intro page slider 1"}', NULL, 0),
(8, 'intro-slider', 0, 'no', '2014-11-18 13:59:00', '2015-12-18 00:00:00', 'High above the <span class="bold">expectations</span>', '', '{"subtitle":"We offer cloud-based combination of mobile apps and digital services which improve the total customer experience and end-user satisfaction.","link":"\\/en\\/home","link_target":"_self","button_text":"","css_id":"","css_text":"","img_p":"\\/images\\/slider\\/intro-slider\\/intro-image-2\\/intro-image-2_l.jpg","img_l":"\\/images\\/slider\\/intro-slider\\/intro-image-2\\/intro-image-2_l.jpg","img_1920":"\\/images\\/slider\\/intro-slider\\/intro-image-2\\/intro-image-2_l.jpg","image_alt":"Intro page slider 2"}', NULL, 0),
(9, 'intro-slider', 0, 'no', '2014-11-18 13:59:00', '2015-12-18 00:00:00', 'Meet our partners'' <span class="bold">milestones</span>', '', '{"subtitle":"Together we design your roadmap! With our partner program you choose, decide and design your business solutions and packages easily. ","link":"\\/en\\/home","link_target":"_self","button_text":"","css_id":"","css_text":"","img_p":"\\/images\\/slider\\/intro-slider\\/intro-image-3\\/intro-image-3_l.jpg","img_l":"\\/images\\/slider\\/intro-slider\\/intro-image-3\\/intro-image-3_l.jpg","img_1920":"\\/images\\/slider\\/intro-slider\\/intro-image-3\\/intro-image-3_l.jpg","image_alt":"Intro page slider 3"}', NULL, 0),
(10, 'intro-slider', 0, 'no', '2014-11-18 13:59:00', '2015-12-18 00:00:00', 'Maintain tight <span class="bold">relationships</span>', '', '{"subtitle":"A well-defined, executable and measurable cross-media strategy provides you with competitive advantage in your overall business workflow.","link":"\\/en\\/home","link_target":"_self","button_text":"","css_id":"","css_text":"","img_p":"\\/images\\/slider\\/intro-slider\\/intro-image-4\\/intro-image-4_l.jpg","img_l":"\\/images\\/slider\\/intro-slider\\/intro-image-4\\/intro-image-4_l.jpg","img_1920":"\\/images\\/slider\\/intro-slider\\/intro-image-4\\/intro-image-4_l.jpg","image_alt":"Intro page slider 4"}', NULL, 0),
(11, 'intro-slider', 0, 'no', '2014-11-18 13:59:00', '2015-12-18 00:00:00', 'Make our goals <span class="bold">sustainable</span>', '', '{"subtitle":"HORISEN has grown into a large business thanks to hundreds of satisfied clients and partners which businesses are constantly developing.","link":"\\/en\\/home","link_target":"_self","button_text":"","css_id":"","css_text":"","img_p":"\\/images\\/slider\\/intro-slider\\/intro-image-5\\/intro-image-5_l.jpg","img_l":"\\/images\\/slider\\/intro-slider\\/intro-image-5\\/intro-image-5_l.jpg","img_1920":"\\/images\\/slider\\/intro-slider\\/intro-image-5\\/intro-image-5_l.jpg","image_alt":"Intro page slider 5"}', NULL, 0);
