(1, 'en', 1, 'Products', '{"subtitle":"","link":"\\/en\\/products\\/icard","link_target":"_self","text":"<p>Shape and combine offline and online visitor experience! By using different products developed by HORISEN, you can easily reach desired business potential and engage different customers. With more than useful SMS services that are still widely-used, through always popular social media products that are proven to increase website traffic and overall conversion process (visitor to customer), we offer you modern and integrated customer loyalty system: the invisible customer card for more purchases and customer retention.<br \\/>Among numerous products, we emphasize:<\\/p>\\r\\n<ul>\\r\\n    <li><a href=\\"\\/en\\/products\\/icard\\">The new iCard customer loyalty program<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n    <li><a href=\\"\\/en\\/products\\/megapromo\\">Megapromo web campaigns<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n    <li><a href=\\"\\/en\\/products\\/smspark\\">SMS &amp; Park solution<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n    <li><a href=\\"\\/en\\/products\\/smswin\\">SMS &amp; Win as a highly-viral service <\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n    <li><a href=\\"\\/en\\/products\\/smswin\\">MFA: Facebook fan page apps <\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n    <li><a href=\\"\\/en\\/products\\/callpay\\">Call &amp; Pay: the fastest payment solution<\\/a<\\/li>\\r\\n    <li><a href=\\"\\/en\\/products\\/internet-apps\\">Intranet Apps<\\/a><\\/li>\\r\\n<\\/ul>","img_960_2x":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser1\\/produkte\\/produkte_960_2x.jpg","img_960":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser1\\/produkte\\/produkte_960.jpg","img_768_2x":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser1\\/produkte\\/produkte_768_2x.jpg","img_768":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser1\\/produkte\\/produkte_768.jpg","img_480_2x":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser1\\/produkte\\/produkte_480_2x.jpg","img_480":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser1\\/produkte\\/produkte_480.jpg","img_320_2x":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser1\\/produkte\\/produkte_320_2x.jpg","img_320":"\\/images\\/teaser\\/teaser1\\/produkte\\/produkte_320.jpg","image_alt":